thread.title: Denis S
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Denis S

author: Denis S
title: Denis S
text: No complaint with quality, having used 'Ink Station' for the first time. Price was comparable with competition. Delivery time was only fair considering the charge was equal with Australia Express Post which is usually overnight in capital cities. Obtaining fast delivery is where people are often forced to shop locally despite price point.
